title: Alexander Vidal Ceballos
text: Manuel Alexander Vidal Ceballos (born 2 September 1996) is a <a href="Dominican%20Republic">Dominican</a> <a href="association%20football">footballer</a> who plays as a <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29%23Centre-back">central defender</a> for <a href="Atletico%20De%20San%20Francisco">Atletico De San Francisco</a> and the <a href="Dominican%20Republic%20national%20football%20team">Dominican Republic national team</a>.
